cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with training deep neural networks for facial expression and emotion recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of an extended loss function, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The test bed application used in the paper is emotion recognition, which is a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
